Communication Module for BBB

BBB as server:

1) Initiate the server on the BBB using
./server <PortNr>
2) Connect to BBB using
./client <BBBipAddress> <PortNr>

BBB as client:

Throught virtual machine there seems to be some IP-issues. It is therefore
recommended to use the BBB as server and apply a static IP address to it.
